-- MOVES-Fabian Herzog joins Carmignac's Swiss business development team
-- 
-- Wed Sep 03, 2014 05:36AM EDT
-- None



Sept 3 (Reuters) - European asset management firm Carmignac Group said it hired Fabian Herzog as a business development manager in its Switzerland team.

Herzog will report to Marco Fiorini, head of country for Switzerland, Carmignac said in a statement.  Herzog, who has 18 years of experience, will focus on private bankers and other third party channels in the German speaking part of the country.